var MapView=function(){let map;function waitForGoogleMaps(callback){window.google&&window.google.maps&&"function"==typeof google.maps.Map?callback():setTimeout((()=>waitForGoogleMaps(callback)),100)}return{methods:{},events:{initEventListeners:function(){const dataElement=document.getElementById("map-data");if(dataElement){const mapData=JSON.parse(dataElement.textContent);waitForGoogleMaps((()=>async function(data){const{lat:lat,lng:lng,location_name:location_name,map_id:map_id}=data,mapContainer=document.getElementById("map-container");map=new google.maps.Map(mapContainer,{scrollwheel:!1,draggable:!0,disableDoubleClickZoom:!0,zoomControl:!1,zoom:16,center:{lat:lat,lng:lng},mapId:map_id});const{AdvancedMarkerElement}=await google.maps.importLibrary("marker");new AdvancedMarkerElement({position:{lat:lat,lng:lng},map:map,title:location_name})}(mapData)))}}}}}();window.MapView=MapView,setTimeout((()=>{MapView.events.initEventListeners()}),200);